snippet.title: FFMAI 2025 | BR Main Event - Week 2 | Day 1 | Group B & C
snippet.description:
🔥 BR মেইন ইভেন্ট শুরু ডে ১ এখন লাইভ 🔥

প্লে-ইনস পর্ব শেষে সেরা টিমগুলো এখন হাজির FFMAI 2025 এর মেইন ইভেন্টে। এখান থেকেই শুরু আসল লড়াই। এখানে টিকে থাকে শুধু ধারাবাহিক, নির্ভীক আর স্ট্র্যাটেজি অনুসরণকারী টিমগুলো।

আজ থেকে লিডারবোর্ড একদম নতুন। প্রতিটা পয়েন্ট, প্রতিটা ফাইট, একটা নতুন ম্যাসেজ । একটা ভুলই বদলে দিতে পারে পুরো ফলাফল।

মেইন ইভেন্টের ওপেনিং ম্যাচে আজ মুখোমুখি হচ্ছে
গ্রুপ B বনাম গ্রুপ C।

আজ খেলবে
Group B: REVENANT XSPARK, NIGHTMARE ESPORTS, IQOO TOTAL GAMING ESPORTS, GOW ESPORTS, KAGENDRA, RED HAWKS
Group C: META NINZA, S8ULELITE, P ESPORTS, BIGETRON BY VITALITY, MAQNA ESPORTS CLUB, DRS GAMING

অ্যারেনার উত্তেজনা চূড়ায়, ফ্যানদের এনার্জিও সর্বোচ্চ। FFMAI 2025 চ্যাম্পিয়ন হওয়ার পথ আজ থেকেই শুরু।

১২ টিম। এক বিশাল ওপেনিং ফাইট। মেইন ইভেন্ট শুরু এখনই! 👑

snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

“Supergirl,” DC Studios’ newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, “Supergirl,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

Audio Credits:

Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)

Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)

Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)

Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‘Inaam’ the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa
